item.title: How can i change the teleport places in the emote place?
item.dc:creator: @mojo4sho mojo4sho
item.description:
@mojo4sho wrote:

i can help you it is very simple lets say the emote is “hell” well find out where the cords take you and write them down.then go to your client.java and press Ctrl-f then put in the x of the cords go till you see

example:
//hell telex:9999
teley:9999
then change the cords to where you want to go then press ctrl-f again and put in hell but remember to change the up or down thing under bar to up
